<title>CANADA: Eicon Technology Corp sees Q3 shr loss.</title>
<headline>Eicon Technology Corp sees Q3 shr loss.</headline>
<dateline>MONTREAL 1997-04-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Eicon Technology Corp said on Tuesday it expects to report a loss of about C$0.06 per share for the third quarter ended March 31.</p>
<p>Sales are expected to be up five percent at C$27.5 million compared to last year's third quarter. But it is lower than the company's expectations, Eicon said in a statement.</p>
<p>&quot;At this level, this will result in a loss of approximately C$0.06 per share for the quarter,&quot; the statement said.</p>
<p>Final third quarter results are expected to be announced by the end of next week.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8100))</p>
